title: Garth Ennis: The Boys 01-18 (Dynamite|2007-09|Dgtl-1280|Empire)
description:
As requested. Though, considering that these releases are Lo-Res and don't seem to contain anything that's missing from Empire's Hi-Res Omnibus, I can't honestly say as I entirely see the point! :P

There's supposed to be an official "(fixed)" version of issue three, which I was not able to locate; instead, I checked the original against Volume One and repaired the (page order) problem myself. Both versions are included, as is a bonus variant cover.
